OL,9,FSophie Pearce waited 14 years to be
OL,10,Fdiagnosed with Ulcerative Colitis.
OL,12,FDespite enduring severe symptoms,
OL,13,Fincluding losing a significant amount
OL,14,Fof blood and experiencing the urgency
OL,15,Fto use the toilet up to 30 times a
OL,16,Fday, Sophie was repeatedly told
OL,17,Fnothing was wrong. It wasn't until she
OL,18,Fhemorrhaged at home and was rushed to
OL,19,FA&E that she finally received a
OL,20,Fdiagnosis.
