OL,7,F"They rushed me straight through, took
OL,8,Fme down to theatre, did a scope, and
OL,9,Fthe consultant that spoke to me as I
OL,10,Fcame round from that said to me, this
OL,11,Fis the worst inflammatory bowel
OL,12,Fdisease, ulcerative colitis I have
OL,13,Fever seen," Sophie said.
OL,15,FThe emergency care support worker, has
OL,16,Fsince undergone surgery to have her
OL,17,Fbowel removed, as well as a
OL,18,Fproctectomy, a procedure in which the
OL,19,Frectum and anus are permanently
OL,20,Fremoved and sealed.
