OL,7,F'If they didn't remove my bowel, I'd
OL,8,Fhave four weeks to live before the
OL,9,Fdisease could kill me'
OL,11,FSophie now says she feels that if her
OL,12,Fsymptoms weren't ignored and the
OL,13,Fdisease had been managed sooner, her
OL,14,Fsurgery may have been avoided.
