OL,7,FEach year, 25,000 people in the UK are
OL,8,Fdiagnosed with Inflammatory Bowel
OL,9,FDisease (IBD), which includes Crohn's
OL,10,FDisease and Ulcerative Colitis. IBD is
OL,11,Fan auto-immune disease where the
OL,12,Fpatient's immune system mistakenly
OL,13,Fattacks the digestive tract, causing
OL,14,Finflammation and ulcers. Crohn's
OL,15,FDisease can affect any part of the
OL,16,Fgastrointestinal tract, while
OL,17,FUlcerative Colitis primarily impacts
OL,18,Fthe colon and rectum. It's a life-long
OL,19,Fillness with no cure.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
