OL,7,FAccording to the report, the quality
OL,8,Fof patient care has declined
OL,9,Fsignificantly since 2019, with a third
OL,10,Fof adults with the disease rating
OL,11,Ftheir care as poor. While nearly a
OL,12,Fquarter of adults reported finding it
OL,13,Fhard to cope with the disease.
OL,15,FSinger song-writer Tom Speight, who
OL,16,Fhas lived with Crohn's disease for the
OL,17,Fpast 20 years, was one of those who
OL,18,Ffound the disease difficult to manage
OL,19,Fafter getting a diagnosis.
